OL,5,Casylum centre
OL,7,FContamination at a former airbase
OL,8,Fearmarked to house asylum seekers
OL,9,Fposes a "potential risk to human
OL,10,Fhealth", according to government
OL,11,Fdocuments.
OL,13,FRAF Scampton, in Lincolnshire, is due
OL,14,Fto be used as accommodation for
OL,15,Fmigrants under plans to bring down the
OL,16,Fnational backlog in asylum claims.
