OL,7,FBut in a letter to West Lindsey
OL,8,FDistrict Council, planning minister
OL,9,FLee Rowley said risks from ground
OL,10,Fgases and unexploded munitions could
OL,11,Fmean the site is unsuitable.
OL,13,FIt said: "Potential risks to human
OL,14,Fhealth arising from ground gases,
OL,15,Funexploded ordnance and ground
OL,16,Fcontamination have been identified
OL,17,Fwhich could affect construction
OL,18,Fworkers, service users and other
OL,19,Fworkers during both the construction
OL,20,Fand operation of the project.
