OL,7,F"These risks could mean the site is
OL,8,Fnot suitable for its intended use
OL,9,Fwhich could give rise to likely
OL,10,Fsignificant effects associated with
OL,11,Fhuman health."
OL,13,FThe letter adds that measures will be
OL,14,Fput in place to make the site safe and
OL,15,Fthe risks are "not likely to be
OL,16,Fsignificant".
