OL,4,Ccontamination 'risk' at proposed
OL,5,Casylum centre
OL,7,FOnce home to the famous Dambusters
OL,8,Fsquadron during the Second World War
OL,9,Fand later the Red Arrows aerobatics
OL,10,Fteam, RAF Scampton has been at the
OL,11,Fcentre of a long-running row over its
OL,12,Ffuture use.
OL,14,FA #300million plan had been drawn up
OL,15,Fto redevelop the site.
OL,17,FBut the Home Office wants permission
OL,18,Fto house potentially hundreds of
OL,19,Fmigrants.
