OL,3,CGovernment letter reveals
OL,4,Ccontamination 'risk' at proposed
OL,5,Casylum centre
OL,7,FCampaigners trying to block its
OL,8,Fconversion into a base for asylum
OL,9,Fseekers say the letter from Mr Rowley
OL,10,Fconfirms what they already knew.
OL,12,FLocal resident Sarah Carter said:
OL,13,F"It's common knowledge that chemicals
OL,14,Fwere used on the planes and there's
OL,15,Fpotential of quite a lot of
OL,16,Fcontaminates there. We've known about
OL,17,Fthis for quite a long time, it's not
OL,18,Fnews to the Home Office. It's not
OL,19,Fsuitable."JIn a statement the Home
OL,20,FOffice said the safety of people on
OL,21,Fsite was the "absolute priority".
